{
  "stem": "13258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My father went to the market there, which was, in a way, important-- Rudnik on the River San-- because later on, a physician from there was our caretaker in a way.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then the train went for a few miles farther.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then the machinist said, I live in that village.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the next bridge, about a few miles away has been destroyed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So the train isn't going any farther.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So you do what you want, I'm going home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He just left the train sitting there in the middle of the tracks?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He left-- he extinguished-- there's a fire in there because it was steam locomotives-- extinguished the fire in the locomotive, let the steam out, and went home.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went in the fields.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were hiding from the German planes that were flying over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And came in up to a, a little town called Stalowa Wola-- which means steel will, 'will' from-- not well, but from 'to want something'-- which was an industrial center the Poles built to have something-- just be farther away from the border.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there, some people offered us to buy some horses to go away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we declined.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then some other people offered us to take us in a car with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was employees from an oil company who were going to their headquarters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were already three people in the car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was full of luggage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we paid a princely sum to be taken to the city of Lublin [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and never got there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We saw-- that's when I really saw, for the first time, war damages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We came through a little town, Janow Lubelski, J-A-N-O with a dash, W, and then dash, Lubelski, L-U-B-E-L-S-K-I.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there, a lumberyard was burning.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
